Description:
    Creates a new Angular directive

Example:
    yo angular-feature:directive thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create:
        app/scripts/directives/thing.js

    This will create (division by component):
        app/scripts/directives/thing.js

    or (division by feature):
    	app/src/common/directives/thing.js


    yo angular-feature:directive foo/thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/directives/thing.js


    yo angular-feature:directive foo/bar/thing [--coffee] [--minsafe]

    This will create (division by feature):
        app/src/foo/bar/directives/thing.js